{"tid":1886133,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"重睇《十年》有感：失去最多嘅係信任","createTime":"2020-02-18T17:55:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T19:53:35.000Z","uid":33586,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5cc6c32d9f16942a205f032a94cc204a892580de","tid":1886133,"uid":33586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T17:55:52.000Z","msg":"今日見呢2日好多人圍插6號同LMK<br />\n我同意佢地係抵屌 特別係6號講沙士源頭係香港同LMK篇回覆<br />\n不過坦白講佢地都係明星仔 二打六 <br />\n佢地澄清完 道完歉咪算數囉 <br />\n見有啲人將黃圈嘅門檻提高到一個太高嘅水平 其實反而無助運動嘅延續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5apQJd0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5apQJd0.jpg&h=390e0a76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無表態咪唔特別估佢嘅顏色 最多唔睇佢嘅節目 唔支持佢 （就好似黃子華）<br />\n當然6號背後係CCTVB就<span style=\"color: red;\">請大家繼續 <strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">支持抵制tvb戰線</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果淨係攻擊班二打六，倒不如主力對付個班狗，仲有同狗私相授授嘅藍屍廢老偽人 <br />\n<br />\n請大家幫幫手<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 對抗藍屍KOL100計劃 的 簡單行動出爐</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1882776/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1882776/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n除此之外，<strong>做下文宣，關注下浮屍，twitter戰線</strong>都要大家幫手<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好話場運動好似完咗，而家大家係自己個範圍可以做到幾多</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"9dbd52e56077edd70775ec914dfb3312fb0b5079","tid":1886133,"uid":33586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T18:01:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d2f879f12ba55d60a05c454cf5a7985737289623","tid":1886133,"uid":33586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T18:07:10.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"384e2db4f9c2a1e4e0090b391